criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Fluent in English, willing and able to read, understand, and sign the informed consent
             form (ICF);

          -  Ability to complete the course of the study and comply with instructions;

          -  Females aged 18 to 40 years, in good general health as deemed by the investigator (no
             physical required);

          -  Individuals free of any systemic or dermatological disorder, tatoos in the testing
             area or recent tanning bed exposure

          -  Anticipated ability to complete the course of the study and to comply with
             instructions;

          -  Females practicing an acceptable method of birth control

          -  Caucasian individuals with Fitzpatrick skin type I, II, or III
